<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV71">
<l>vaṇṭulāvu kōtaimātar kāraṇatti ṉālvekuṇ</l>
<l>ṭiṇṭavāṇa ṉīraiññūṟu tōḷkaḷaittu ṇittanāḷ</l>
<l>muṇṭaṉīṟaṉ makkaḷveppu mōṭiyaṅki yōṭiṭak</l>
<l>kaṇṭunāṇi vāṇaṉukki raṅkiṉāṉem māyaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The day [He] severed the thousand arms of Bāṇa—who, furious</l>
<l>Due to the girl [like] a creeper swarmed by bees—came together [with the gods],</l>
<l>Our Wonderful [Lord] felt pity for Bāṇa, being embarrassed,</l>
<l>seeing that the shaven-headed, ash[-besmeared Śiva], [his] sons, the god of fevers,</l>
<l rend="indent">Durgā, [and] the fire god ran away!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
